data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with an inground pool is located in a prime location within close proximity to Lake Elbert. The enclosed porch welcomes you into the home and leads to the spacious living and dining areas. The oversized family room is perfect for entertaining and relaxation. The 3 bedrooms are located down the hallway and are split by a bathroom. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and a pantry for added storage. The second bathroom is conveniently located adjacent to the kitchen and the large 15 x 30 screened back porch, which overlooks the fenced-in back yard and recently resurfaced inground chlorine pool. Additional storage space is provided by the sheds in the backyard. Recent upgrades include a new roof and HVAC installed within the last 2 years. This home is conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, and the beautiful Lake Elbert.
